data.description:
Reduced Price! 
Welcome to this stunning 2-story home boasting 2,529 square feet of living space, featuring four bedrooms, three full baths, and a 2-car garage. Situated in the beautiful community of Provence within Meadow Pointe IV in Wesley Chapel, this home offers a perfect blend of space and style. It is located on a quiet cul-de-sac street.
As you enter, a spacious foyer invites you into the beautiful eat-in kitchen, equipped with dark wood cabinets, coordinating stainless steel appliances, a convenient walk-in pantry, and a breakfast bar. The kitchen flows seamlessly into the great room, providing an ideal space for an entertainment center or a large-screen TV. Sliders open to a covered patio and the backyard, perfect for outdoor relaxation and entertainment.
The first floor also includes a bedroom and a full bath, making it an excellent space for guests or a versatile room that could serve as a den, office, or craft room tailored to your family's needs.
Upstairs, you'll find a welcoming loft area, the spacious main suite with a walk-in closet, a bath with a wood vanity, and two separate sinks. Additionally, there are three secondary bedrooms and another full bath on this level, ensuring plenty of space for the entire family.
Meadow Pointe IV offers fantastic amenities for all to enjoy, including a pool, basketball, Fitness Center, tennis courts, and a playground. This is truly a family-friendly community waiting to welcome your family.
Conveniently located near I-75, 275, Wiregrass Mall, Tampa Premium Outlets, restaurants, schools, and hospitals, this home offers easy access to all your daily needs. 
Don't miss this opportunity; call us today to schedule a private viewing.
